cc:Work.dc:title: Booze Frame
cc:Work.dc:description: Somewhere someone wants a fancy frame with beer on the bottom to invite their friends to a beer drinking party. The time has come that the desired frame be made available! This was actually quite a headache to synthesize (the old advert covered important parts of the frame and etc) and I'm not sure it was worth it because this is a very niche value frame. None the less, enjoy!
